summary: This is a game save which will allow you to step into "Artemisia's shoes", just copy paste the save to: My Documents -> My games -> Skyrim -> Saves, and enjoy !
descriptionHtml:
This is a character edited at 1024x768 resolution, if you have a better laptop/pc and you can run Skyrim at higher resolutions, it may affect the way she looks like.

~ Required mods for Artemisia's look:

1. ApachiiSkyHair http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/10168/?
2. Calientes Beautiful Bodies Edition -CBBE- http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2666/?
3. Better Females By Bella Natural Edition (CBBE No Make Up - file) http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/26113/?
4. Skyrim script extender http://skse.silverlock.org/
5. Enhanced character edit http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/12951/?
6. No more blocky faces http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/30/?
7. The eyes of beauty http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/13722/?
8. Xenius character enhancement http://www.nexusmods.com/skyrim/mods/2356/?
